data.title: Marvin Williams: The Perfect Teammate
data.meta_description: By Sam Perley, hornets.com You don’t see too many players in the NBA put up career seasons in their 11th year in the league but that’s exactly what Hornets forward Marvin Williams was able to accomplish during an extremely successful 2015-16 campaign for the Charlotte Hornets. Fresh off signing a four-year extension with the organization this past summer, Williams is picking up right where he left off amidst the team’s franchise-record-setting start to the season.
